{"id": 3275, "title": "Ticket #3275: Condor-CE", "description": "<blockquote>\nThis ticket summarizes the work required to implement the HTCondor-CE on the OSG.\n\n<p><span class=\"subsection\"></span></p><h3>Major Tasks</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Improve blahp file handling (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3276\" title=\"Improve blahp file handling\">#3276</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3377\" title=\"gridmanager reports poor hold message for blahp failure\">#3377</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3383\" title=\"Blahp requires HOME to be set in the environment\">#3383</a></span>)\n</li><li>Improve logging of security information for WLCG traceability requirements\n</li><li>Verify HTCondor-C functionality (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3384\" title=\"Verify HTCondor-CE functionality\">#3384</a></span>)\n</li><li>Verify batch system profiles (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"tktview?tn=3399\" title=\"Documentation missing for batch GAHP attributes\">#3399</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3398\" title=\"Batch GAHP cannot set remote memory or walltime requests\">#3398</a></span>)\n</li><li>Usability and packaging (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3370\" title=\"condor_submit attempts (incorrectly) to set remote owner\">#3370</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3371\" title=\"Create authorization ping tool\">#3371</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"active\" href=\"tktview?tn=3056\" title=\"Schedd should automatically trigger a reschedule when job goes idle\">#3056</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=3380\" title=\"Foolproof mechanism for JobRouter routes\">#3380</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"tktview?tn=3081\" title=\"Disable tra